2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to improve the accuracy of object counting using constrained multi-stage CNNs. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep learning techniques to improve the accuracy of object counting. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with object counting in surveillance scenes, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still relevant as object counting is an important task in robotics applications such as autonomous navigation and object recognition.
